import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-home', templateUrl: './home.component.html', styleUrls: ['./home.component.css'], }) export class HomeComponent { ngOnInit() { this.service.isSignedIn$.subscribe((status) => { this.login = status; if (this.login == false) { this.router.navigate(['/logIn']); } }); } }
